Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}距今100年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}出現了人類的天敵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們與人類之間存在著壓倒性的力量差距
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類差點陷入滅絕的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}存活下來的人類們建造了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}瑪利亞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}羅塞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}席納之牆 三面城牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從此實現了100年的和平生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.07,0:00:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在受到巨人襲擊的托洛斯特區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士兵們之所以會受害如此嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也是因為精銳的調查軍團不在的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們在那天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才剛出去牆外調查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是調查軍團的主力部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾爾文團長 請你們把巨人全都殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.23,0:02:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快看是里維士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他可是一個人的戰力就抵得過一個旅團
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}呿 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家充滿羨慕的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果知道了你這有潔癖的個性 一定會幻滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個外面...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就有著巨人們...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次能遇到怎樣的巨人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果奇行種出來的話就太棒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果是奇行種的話這裡就有一隻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}牆外調查以及為了放置補給物資而設置據點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被託付這個任務的調查軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是人類智慧的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為某些才能智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}才使得生存率大幅提昇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}即使如此每次派兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是會造成超過三成以上的人員損失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.49,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}Day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.82,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}We have lost our edge
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:42.09,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}Don't you know
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:44.79,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}Forgotten is the life we led
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:45.98,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}Now it seems
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.54,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}You don't care what the risk is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:52.34,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}The peaceful times have made us blind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:53.57,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}Can't look back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.87,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}They will not come back
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:57.18,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}Can't be afarid
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.46,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}It's time after time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:00.98,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}So once again
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:03.62,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}I'm hiding in my room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:07.68,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}The peaceful times have made us blind
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:11.43,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}So you can't fly if never try
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:15.16,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}You told me... Oh, Long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.14,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}but you left the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.03,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}Out side the gate
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:21.84,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}So more than ever, It's real
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.74,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}It was like a nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:26.28,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}Now it's painful for me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:30.06,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}Because nobody wants to die too fast
