Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:22.13,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}Oh Give me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:22.13,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}Our life is so short
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:22.13,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}Song for the reluctant heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:22.13,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}I wanna be brave like you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:22.13,SP-EG,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}From my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.49,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}日復一日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.82,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}我們失去了底限
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:42.09,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}你可知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:44.79,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}被遺忘是我們生命的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:45.98,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}你似乎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.54,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}不在乎風險是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:52.34,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}和平的時光讓我們盲目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:53.57,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}不能回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.87,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}他們不會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:57.18,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}不能害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.46,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}總是屢屢復返
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:00.98,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}所以再一次地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:03.62,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}我躲在我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:07.68,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}和平的時光讓我們盲目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:11.43,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}"你不嘗試的話永遠沒辦法飛翔"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:15.16,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}你這樣告訴我...噢, 好久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.14,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}但是你離開了城牆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.03,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}出了大門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:21.84,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}這比什麼都還真實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.74,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}這就像一場惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:26.28,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}此刻對我來說痛苦無比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:30.06,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}因為沒有人想英年早逝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:32.01,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}想起悲傷的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:33.84,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}此刻對我來說痛苦無比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.81,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}我能看見你的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.74,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}我能聽見你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:39.47,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}想起我們相遇的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:41.35,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}此刻對我來說痛苦無比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:45.15,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}因為沒有人想英年早逝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.17,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}想起我們夢想的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.98,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}而這對我來說痛苦無比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:50.85,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}我能看見你的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.25,SP-CH,Lyric,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(250,250)\be5}我能聽見你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而人類跟巨人之間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}依然存在著「實力」的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我看著...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然現在你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想要消滅人類...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過到最後存活下來的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}依然還是人類...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們這些傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一定會...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}被里維士官長...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}右側一個...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}左側兩個...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}增援已經陸續聚集了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}佩托拉 妳去救出底下的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剩下的人全部去支援右翼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我去解決左側的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不會讓你太痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次換我這了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對吧 不痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}每個都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我擺出一臉有趣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我乖一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不然我就沒辦法將你的肉...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}整齊地割下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}髒死了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}血...止不住...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官...長...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對人類是否有所貢獻了...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是我會就這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼都沒貢獻地...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}死去呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你已經表現的非常好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從今以後也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你所留下來的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將會賦予我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我跟你約定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我一定 會將巨人消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他已經...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這傢伙 他有聽到最後嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他一定聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他看起來很安詳地睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}里維
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}撤退?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都還沒有推進到極限呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道要我的部下白白地犧牲嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人一起以城鎮為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就跟五年前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}城鎮似乎發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}城牆可能又被破壞了也說不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...不應該是這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們跟五年前不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}拚命地訓練了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}拚命地思考著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了戰勝他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了不被他們吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好熱...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好熱...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}救救我...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}救...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼會這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼我們還是被剝奪了...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}生命也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}夢想也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我怎麼可以就這樣放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要殺光他們...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一隻不留地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:09:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}用我...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這雙手...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我要殺光他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從這世上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一隻不留地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我還要...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我還要...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我還要殺更多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想殺更多...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還要...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}更多...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}殺掉你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 身體還能動嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}意識還清楚嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把你知道的事情全部說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們一定可以了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聽到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他說要「殺你們」...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是啊 的確是聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那傢伙打算要把我們都吃光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家在說什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那個劍是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是指向我們嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那不是用來打倒巨人的武器嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼要用那種眼神看我?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是... 怎樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}訓練兵帶好自己的裝備待命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.49,0:12:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}後來好不容易才拿到瓦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從托洛斯特逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有這種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好幾次志願想替大家進行補給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們好不容易才拿到瓦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那...那麼現在不在這裡的人全部都....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}連那個米卡莎也是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不 我想米卡莎是跟約翰他們一起過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道米卡莎受傷了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們被下了保密命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}保密命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那是什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}反正那原本就是瞞不住的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很快的 全人類都會知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果到時候... 還有人類的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人本身會以肉體來做為防護壁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這點技術科也考慮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但我們依然不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}畢竟這裡是人類與巨人的最前線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.66,Default,*,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一分一秒都不能鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}任務方面沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是 我倒比較擔心負責前線的同伴們的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剛剛的傳令兵也是一臉蒼白的往本部移動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是我們只要專心按照當初訓練的 來迎戰就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我聽說五年前和漢尼斯隊長一起逃出來的那三個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如今都成了訓練兵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們也在最前線...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不好意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不該說太多的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}每個人都有自己一套存活的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一個擁有高超的戰鬥技術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一個具有強韌的精神力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而另一個則有著聰明的頭腦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們一定還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}葉卡訓練兵!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以及旁邊的阿卡曼和亞魯雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剛才你們所做的 是背叛人類的行為!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們將以你們的性命來審問你!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果敢再說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}或是想要逃離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我將會立刻朝你發射榴彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒有打算手下留情!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我就直接問了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你的真實身分到底是什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是人類嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是巨人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是什麼問題...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是什麼眼神?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}彷彿在看著怪物似地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道是要我說「我是」嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不懂你問這個的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還想裝傻嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你這怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有本事你再試一次看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我會把你一瞬間轟成渣!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓你沒時間露出真面目!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真面目?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很多人都看到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你從巨人體內出現的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們人類竟然讓你這種來路不明的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}入侵到羅塞之牆裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算你們是國王授予的訓練兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在出現風險的早期就應該加以排除
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我這麼做並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}說不定當初破壞瑪利亞之牆的那個盔甲巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在還會出現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}目前是我們人類存亡的危機關頭!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}了解了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們不能為了你們再分散兵力和時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我將會毫不猶豫地對你發射榴彈砲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}的確 他們的態度很明顯是在反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且看來是得不到什麼有用的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說的對 這只是在浪費兵力和時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在簡單多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要在他化為人類的這段期間內殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.90,0:17:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我的特長是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把肉削下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果有必要我隨時可以露一手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}倘若有人想體驗一下我的特長的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那就請他先站上前來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}隊長 那位米卡莎．阿卡曼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.59,0:17:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}原本跟著我們這些精銳負責後衛的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}她的表現足以抵過一百名士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果失去她對人類來說會是一大損失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 米卡莎 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:17:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎 妳怎麼會和人類對抗呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這狹小的牆壁中 我們到底能夠往哪裡逃啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不管要我對付誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我都會阻止艾連被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}除此之外都不解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.93,0:18:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們要溝通!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家都還不清楚狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以才會陷入恐慌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道只有我認為自己不是巨人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒有到目前為止的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}身體完全無力站不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要是亂開口又可能會沒命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我會被人類殺掉?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這種荒唐的事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}況且到底是怎樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我從巨人的體內跑出來?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底在說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到底是怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道那不是夢嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這沒衣服覆蓋的部分可是有長著手的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這不就跟巨人一樣了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼可能...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼我會...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我再問一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你的真實身分到底是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之 我絕對不能回答錯誤...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不然會死的可不只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.71,0:19:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我從以前就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跟你們一樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是人類!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那可就別怪我了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是不得已的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為誰都無法證明...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}自己是不是惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}往上面跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別這樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我就給你看看我一直把它當作是秘密的地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這把鑰匙你要寸不離身地隨時帶著它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且你每次看到這把鑰匙就要想到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你必須去地下室這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為打針的關係 你會產生記憶障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以現在說明也沒有用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聽好 奪回瑪利亞之牆之後你一定要去地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這股力量到時候會派上用場的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:21:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我想他們的記憶會教你如何去使用它的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你總有一天到了地下室就會了解到真相的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然那是條艱苛的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但你絕對要到那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果你想拯救大家的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就一定要掌控住這股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}幹掉了嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.73,0:23:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連並不是人類的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.91,0:23:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然阿爾敏挺身辯解
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是被恐懼所囚禁而放棄思考的駐紮軍團
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.88,0:24:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}下達了將艾連處刑的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
